  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想做一个关于思维导图本身的思维导图，根节点就叫\"mindmap\"吧，用圆角矩形那种样式。然后第一层我想分成三个方向：起源、研究和工具。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root((mindmap))",
        "Origins",
        "Research",
        "Tools"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，根节点用双圆括号做成圆形样式，下面挂三个一级分支。Origins是讲思维导图的历史渊源吗？Research和Tools的具体内容您有想法吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root((mindmap))",
        "Origins",
        "Research",
        "Tools"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Origins下面放\"Long history\"，强调它有很长的历史。Research这部分我想放两个研究方向：一个是关于思维导图有效性的研究，另一个是关于自动生成的研究。Tools就放传统的纸笔和我们现在用的Mermaid。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Long history",
        "On effectiveness",
        "On Automatic creation",
        "Pen and paper",
        "Mermaid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，Research下面有两个子节点：On effectiveness和On Automatic creation。Tools下面是Pen and paper和Mermaid。我注意到Automatic creation您用的是Automatic而不是Automation，需要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "On Automatic creation",
        "Automatic creation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用改，On Automatic creation这个表达更强调\"自动创建\"这个动作过程，符合学术文献里的说法。结构就这样定吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "On Automatic creation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画好了。根节点是mindmap，三个一级分支Origins、Research、Tools都展开了。Origins下面有Long history；Research下面挂着On effectiveness和On Automatic creation；Tools下面是Pen and paper和Mermaid。您看看整体结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root((mindmap))",
        "Origins",
        "Long history",
        "Research",
        "On effectiveness",
        "On Automatic creation",
        "Tools",
        "Pen and paper",
        "Mermaid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整体没问题，不过Mermaid作为工具节点，和Pen and paper并列在一起，这个对比挺有意思的——从传统纸笔到现代代码绘图。结构就这样，不用再改了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Mermaid",
        "Pen and paper"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，最终版本确认。思维导图的思维导图，三层结构完整，从起源、研究到工具全覆盖。我保存了这个版本。",
